1
00:00:14,930 --> 00:00:22,080
♪In the distant hills, a goose cries
with head bowed, walking alone♪

2
00:00:23,060 --> 00:00:28,340
♪The river reflects
the shadow of longing♪

3
00:00:31,060 --> 00:00:38,170
♪The grass beside me looks up,
searching the sky♪

4
00:00:38,330 --> 00:00:45,570
♪Yet, even the eastbound spring water
cannot drown my heartbeat♪

5
00:00:49,100 --> 00:00:51,940
=Burning Passion=

6
00:00:51,980 --> 00:00:54,940
=Episode 24=

7
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:03,039
I, Shen Qingru, swear to the heavens

8
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:07,040
that there will never be anything

9
00:01:08,040 --> 00:01:09,920
between me and Shen Cheng.

10
00:01:30,599 --> 00:01:31,719
That day in the woodshed.

11
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:33,239
What did you call me?

12
00:01:33,959 --> 00:01:34,879
Call me that again.

13
00:01:39,239 --> 00:01:40,319
Jiang...

14
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:42,879
Jiang Wei.

15
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:48,560
You swore there would never be anything
between you and Shen Cheng.

16
00:01:48,599 --> 00:01:49,920
But I'm Jiang Wei.

17
00:01:51,239 --> 00:01:52,680
What about that vow?

18
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:54,280
It doesn't apply.

19
00:01:59,660 --> 00:02:03,600
♪Papayas picked, the bride is wed♪

20
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:07,621
♪Rouge and powder, the bride applies♪

21
00:02:07,752 --> 00:02:11,752
♪Painting her face white, blushing red♪

22
00:02:11,832 --> 00:02:15,680
♪In her embroidered shoes,
she journeys to distant lands♪

23
00:02:15,890 --> 00:02:19,243
♪To distant lands,
where wild geese take flight♪

24
00:02:19,294 --> 00:02:23,200
♪Oh, they soar,
with no longing to return♪

25
00:02:24,759 --> 00:02:25,719
(Mother.)

26
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,240
(Brother.)

27
00:02:28,759 --> 00:02:31,080
(You can finally rest in peace.)

28
00:02:41,599 --> 00:02:42,759
Jiang Wei.

29
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,599
(The situation is unstable.)

30
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:32,319
(The people are suffering.)

31
00:03:32,879 --> 00:03:36,639
(I'm going to the front lines to fight
and defend the country. Wait for me to return.)

32
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:39,000
(I'm not waiting anymore.)

33
00:03:39,319 --> 00:03:40,520
(I'm going with you.)

34
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:46,080
(Two years later)
Dr. Shen.

35
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:47,840
Please take a look
at the patient in Bed 13.

36
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:49,000
Coming.

37
00:04:22,199 --> 00:04:23,240
Deputy Zhang.

38
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,319
The front line has held,

39
00:04:28,959 --> 00:04:29,839
but...

40
00:04:50,380 --> 00:04:53,180
(My body belongs
to my country and to you.)

41
00:04:56,620 --> 00:04:58,200
(My body belongs
to my country and to you.)

42
00:05:12,923 --> 00:05:20,225
♪In the distant hills, a goose cries
with head bowed, walking alone♪

43
00:05:20,829 --> 00:05:26,189
♪The river reflects
the shadow of longing♪

44
00:05:26,399 --> 00:05:27,480
Jiang Wei...

45
00:05:29,079 --> 00:05:29,959
(Shen Qingru,)

46
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,439
(what am I)

47
00:05:33,839 --> 00:05:35,240
(to you?)

48
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,319
(You...)

49
00:05:38,839 --> 00:05:39,920
(You're my heart.)

50
00:05:40,820 --> 00:05:41,879
(Where are you taking me?)

51
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:42,959
(Away from here.)

52
00:05:43,399 --> 00:05:44,920
(To a place free of the clan laws.)

53
00:05:46,079 --> 00:05:47,399
(If she loses even a single hair,)

54
00:05:48,079 --> 00:05:49,199
(I'll return with my troops)

55
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:50,800
(and flatten Chunshui Town!)

56
00:05:55,639 --> 00:05:56,759
Jiang Wei.

57
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,160
Jiang Wei.

58
00:06:00,218 --> 00:06:08,080
♪Together through love,
we roam until the very end♪

59
00:06:08,232 --> 00:06:15,861
♪My love for you
etched deep within my eyes♪

60
00:06:16,070 --> 00:06:24,087
♪Outside the house, as the woes die down,
I feel your presence♪

61
00:06:24,189 --> 00:06:31,578
♪There is a hope I hold, telling
the wild geese you're still on my mind♪

62
00:06:31,970 --> 00:06:43,840
♪There is a hope I hold, telling
the wild geese you're still on my mind♪

63
00:06:57,639 --> 00:06:58,680
Jiang Xiao.

64
00:06:59,199 --> 00:07:00,040
Qingru.

65
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,240
You're suited up.

66
00:07:04,319 --> 00:07:07,240
The war is raging.
I can't just stand by and watch.

67
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:09,080
The Jiang Family Army isn't the only one

68
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:11,240
who has put aside its past
to fight the enemy together.

