73
00:07:53,956 --> 00:07:57,141
♪To distant lands,
where wild geese take flight♪

74
00:07:57,330 --> 00:08:00,385
♪Oh, they soar,
with no longing to return♪

75
00:08:00,385 --> 00:08:02,940
(Chenpi, Dangshen, Tong Cao, Dang...)

76
00:08:12,620 --> 00:08:20,300
(Dang Gui)

77
00:08:23,639 --> 00:08:25,920
Mother, what is she writing?

78
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,800
The "Gui" in Dang Gui.

79
00:08:31,439 --> 00:08:32,200
All right.

80
00:08:32,279 --> 00:08:34,240
Thank you, Doctor.

81
00:09:01,759 --> 00:09:02,759
Jiang Xiao.

82
00:09:25,636 --> 00:09:31,781
♪When I start missing you again♪

83
00:09:31,818 --> 00:09:35,912
♪I try to slow down time♪

84
00:09:36,574 --> 00:09:39,563
♪That moment of brilliant fireworks♪

85
00:09:40,100 --> 00:09:49,483
♪If only I could truly
do it all over again♪

86
00:09:49,658 --> 00:09:53,803
♪Just once would be enough♪

87
00:09:57,563 --> 00:10:02,210
♪Along the arc of missing you♪

88
00:10:02,261 --> 00:10:04,989
♪I slowly fall♪

89
00:10:05,069 --> 00:10:13,527
♪And I'm lost on a lonely planet
without you♪

90
00:10:16,850 --> 00:10:23,127
♪Please don't look back at me♪

91
00:10:23,505 --> 00:10:27,578
♪I'll be fine♪

92
00:10:31,620 --> 00:10:35,500
(End)

93
